==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Washpot
<hw>Wash"pot`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A pot or
vessel in which anything is washed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Tin-Plate Manuf.)</fld> <def>A pot containing
melted tin into which the plates are dipped to be coated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wash sale</ent>⟦br⟧
